---
source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Export or restore browser state (cookies, localStorage, sessionStorage)

Usage: bl storage [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  restore  Restore browser state from a JSON file
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -o, --output <output>  Output file path
  -v, --verbose          Enable debug logging
      --headless         Hide browser window (visible by default)
      --json             Output as JSON
  -h, --help             Print help

Examples:
  bl storage
  # Print state as JSON

  bl storage -o state.json
  # Save state to file
